reviewText: lo unico que no me gusto que se ve como nuevo pero hay escenas que no puedo ver es lo que unico malo de esto :S si no fuera por que la compre solo por Lorena Rojas hace rato lo botaria ya...

It was great how the weaved in the latin singing groups--That was really great. Love the music, dancing and the club scene. It's a really fun show. Very colorful, light hearted, romantic comedy! Nice collection. Just finished the watching season one and two, and pre-ordered season three.

This a great telenovela without many cuts as it is usually done to the telenovelas genre so you can see and enjoy the whole film from beginning to end. The film is very well made the plot is great and I just cannot wait for the second season to get out. I recommend this film to every telenovelas fans/lovers.
